Encoding: UTF-8
Package: piecepackr
Type: Package
Title: Functions and Rscripts to Build Piecepack Decks
Version: 0.12.0-1
Author: Trevor L Davis. 
Maintainer: Trevor L Davis <trevor.l.davis@gmail.com>
Description: This is an R package designed to make configurable piecepack graphics. It can be used with the grid R package to make piecepack diagrams (i.e. for inclusion in rulesets) and custom Print & Play layouts.
License: CC BY-SA 4.0
URL: https://github.com/trevorld/piecepackr
